cause there aren t any lenses with high enough power to correct their vision. The contact lenses do correct the vision up to a certain degree, but the contact lens powers only go up to a certain point.","Sometimes the reason certain people can t wear contact lenses is because they are allergic to the disinfecting solution or the contact lenses themselves. Every time you would go to clean your contact lenses your body would react negatively and the irritation is usually too uncomfortable to wear the lenses. Some experts even suggest diabetics should stay away from wearing contact lenses because they are prone to infections and their bodies may not tolerate even a mild infection and it may also take longer to cope with it.<br/><br/>"]},"id":"7feae895-a150-4bb1-b8bc-3bc2e8ab050b","type":"text"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["At TopTenREVIEWS We Do the Research So You Don&#39;t Have To. "]},"id":"5cb05981-3fd9-4a75-8664-5b6128059d74","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_4883","url":"/who-shouldn-t-wear-contact-lenses","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"christine-mcgrath","url":"/author/christine-mcgrath","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Christine McGrath","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"2xHmEUm865wbq4PGH4DhbV","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-09-03T15:25:59Z","datePublished":"2010-09-03T15:25:59Z","name":"Who Shouldn't Wear Contact Lenses","synopsis":"The convenience of contacts for eyeglass wearers is indescribable. There is such a freedom to wearing contacts that so many eyeglass wearers desire that freedom.","review":{},"strapline":"The convenience of contacts for eyeglass wearers is indescribable. There is such a freedom to wearing contacts that so many eyeglass wearers desire that freedom.","language":"en","dateModified":"2010-09-03T20:10:03Z","id":"CDByQPGD9Yc5zTGXxuwDQ6","meta":{"title":"Who Shouldn't Wear Contact Lenses","description":"The convenience of contac